    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p><a href=\"https://intrepidgeeks.com/tutorial/understand-the-concept-of-javascript-perjs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">참고</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"peerjs는-무엇인가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#peerjs%EB%8A%94-%EB%AC%B4%EC%97%87%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"peerjs는 무엇인가 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PeerJS는 무엇인가?</h1>\n<p>WebRTC를 활용하여 손쉽게 P2P간 실시간으로 text를 주고받거나 <br>\r\nmedia stream connection을 만들 수 있게해주는 라이브러리로<br>\r\nWebRTC기술을 보다 편리하게 사용할 수 있다</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 484px; \n                width: 100%;\n                box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n              \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/6ad3c/peerjs_logo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.208333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/a59e9/peerjs_logo.webp 192w,\n/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/0ca9f/peerjs_logo.webp 384w,\n/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/e1030/peerjs_logo.webp 484w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/3b721/peerjs_logo.png 192w,\n/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/66595/peerjs_logo.png 384w,\n/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/6ad3c/peerjs_logo.png 484w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/6ad3c/peerjs_logo.png\"\n            alt=\"./peerjs_logo.png\"\n            title=\"./peerjs_logo.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"peerjs세팅\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#peerjs%EC%84%B8%ED%8C%85\" aria-label=\"peerjs세팅 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PeerJS세팅</h1>\n<p><b>Include the Javascript client</b></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://unpkg.com/peerjs@1.3.2/dist/peerjs.min.js\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><b>Create the Peer object (객체 생성)</b></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> peer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Peer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"peerjs-문법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#peerjs-%EB%AC%B8%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"peerjs 문법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PeerJS 문법</h1>\n<p>peerjs객체는 생성될때 unique한 ID값이 할당된다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">peer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'open'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'My peer ID is: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"method\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#method\" aria-label=\"method permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Method</h2>\n<p><b>peer.on</b> - peer이벤트의 listeners를 세팅해줌<br>\r\npeer.on(‘open’) - 커넥션이 연결된 경우<br>\r\npeer.on(‘connection’) - 데이터를 받을 준비가된 상태<br>\r\npeer.on(‘disconnect’) - 원하지 않게 연결이 끊겼을때<br>\r\npeer.on(‘close’) - 연결돼있는 커넥션을 끊어줌<br>\r\npeer.on(‘error’) - 연결중에 에러가 발생한 경우<br></p>\n<p>peer.connect - peer.id값 으로 브라우저간 연결을 할 수 있다<br>\r\npeer.call - 미디어 커넥션할때 사용<br>\r\npeer.disconnect - 모든 커넥션 연결이 해제된 경우<br>\r\npeer.reconnect - 최근 서버에 연결된 peer ID값으로 재연결 시도<br>\r\n오직disconnected된 peer만 시도가능<br>\r\npeer.destroy - 커넥션 연결을 해제한다<br>\r\npeer.id - 다른 peer에 연결할 수 있는 ID값<br>\r\npeer.connections - 할당된 모든 커넥션에 접근가능</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"PeerJS","summary":"PeerJS공부하기","date":"2022.04.05.","categories":["Web","WebRTC","PeerJS"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/59d2a/peerjs_logo.png","srcSet":"/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/9959f/peerjs_logo.png 121w,\n/static/6fc31d067f65b01d8b7b75599a676c9a/9764b/peerjs_logo.png 242w,